# Android release signing secrets — NEVER commit these.
# Real keystore + password files live OUTSIDE the repo (see
# docs/releases/phase-09f-release-signing/RELEASE_SIGNING.md).
# Only android/key.properties.example (placeholders) is tracked.
android/key.properties
key.properties
*.jks
*.keystore
*.p12
*.pem
*.key
